### ============================================
### DivTracker API - Ticker Search
### ============================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### Lookup Symbol - Búsqueda exacta por símbolo
### Recomendado para autocompletado
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickers/lookup?symbol=BAM
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Lookup - Apple
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickers/lookup?symbol=AAPL
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Lookup - Microsoft
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickers/lookup?symbol=MSFT
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Search by Name - Búsqueda fuzzy por nombre
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickers/search?q=apple
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Search - Coca Cola
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickers/search?q=coca%20cola
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Search - Bank
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickers/search?q=bank
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
